{"tid":11093,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[貓撚]養緊貓又試過屋企突然要裝修既既絲打入一入黎","createTime":"2016-11-29T07:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T13:40:15.000Z","uid":13371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b2ed5be5e6fe0e390bd4ca497eb5ea5a4dd6176f","tid":11093,"uid":13371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:20:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n黎近屋企要裝修，又會油牆，又要換新傢私<br />\n屋企會好亂同好多灰塵 所以最近開始諗點安置主人一個星期左右<br />\n<br />\n試過諗比錢啲寵物酒店比主人住 又試過諗問下有養貓既朋友幫我睇住主人一排 但係又怕主人唔適應同好驚（利申：主人好細膽同好怕陌生人）<br />\n<br />\n因為咁我宜家唔知點幫主人安排好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以想問下遇過上面情況既巴打絲打意見 參考下你地會點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n附上主人近照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  希望各位可以比下意見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a826k5S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa826k5S.jpg&h=b7d3433e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qx3X4DL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQx3X4DL.jpg&h=32d34ea4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8755f291791877526af400086700292980de17df","tid":11093,"uid":19159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:22:05.000Z","msg":"首先建立左貓仔同你朋友既感情先 你朋友身上有冇貓味？"},{"pid":"5959469b65b81262e0b9b874bfac2b963481537b","tid":11093,"uid":13371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先建立左貓仔同你朋友既感情先 你朋友身上有冇貓味？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該冇 佢都係見過主人一兩次 佢都有養兩隻貓"},{"pid":"4125787f3564d6e64e3962aa8cf31a62c100d5c3","tid":11093,"uid":19159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:26:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquo